description: Geekbench 3 is Primate Labs' cross-platform processor benchmark, with a new scoring system that separates single-core and multi-core performance, and new workloads that simulate real-world scenarios. Geekbench 3 makes it easier than ever to find out if your computer is up to speed.
summary: Geekbench 3 is Primate Labs' cross-platform processor benchmark.
author: Primate Labs Inc.
